â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ Time: 0 hours
â”‚   â””â”€â”€ Outcome: Compromised â†’ Scenario 3C
â””â”€â”€ Hang Up & Report (GOOD)
    â”œâ”€â”€ Cost: $500
    â”œâ”€â”€ Time: 2 hours
    â””â”€â”€ Outcome: Reported â†’ Scenario 3D
```

